{"tid":168624,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"靜脈曲張治療方法？","createTime":"2017-03-23T16:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T16:09:53.000Z","uid":7749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4dd4d6e63485bdcd5ea54bf2bde56a2d7b17d9b1","tid":168624,"uid":7749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T16:09:53.000Z","msg":"工作需要長時間坐係到 比較少需要站立 一年幾前發現右腳後膝大腿位置有明顯紫紅色血管透到出皮膚 <br />\n近排發現左腳相同位置都開始黎料 有時會痕有時會微微痛 上網睇資料同下圖第一期症狀吻合 而且形態同圖片都一樣 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/24/000748_29ca3939dbb1568fc73229c7bfd3182b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F24%2F000748_29ca3939dbb1568fc73229c7bfd3182b.jpg&h=12230711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想問下有冇巴絲有相同煩惱同埋治療心得？或者做過手術的話係費用幾多？係邊到做？做咩類型手術？定還是普通壓力襪都可以？ 唔好意思太多問題 但有啲驚所以上黎問下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該哂"}]}